    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-8064-8db8-d949cb4e39fb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The availability of resources that now existes makes it really challenging for prospective learners to select the best sets of resources available to them. Authors collect data from providers and use Named Entity Recognition and entity linking to extract information about pre-requisites, learning objectives, etc…",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
