    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-80c7-b469-c13517213213",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "These representations are incorporated into a Knowledge Graph that is used as a basis for a recommender system for career path and upskilling suggestions. Model is evaluated using CareerCoach 2022 gold standard. ",
